{
  "stem": "1753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And about 11:30 or so they stormed the inner camp with their of guns in their hands and came through the main gate in the inner camp and say, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Lay down wherever you are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And people laid down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some magic power [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] gave me a signal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was delirious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I felt that's the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But my subconscious mind led me back into my barrack, jumped out the back window, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ran across the back yard in that area, 20, 30 yards, to a shed where there was a lot of lumber stored.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I crawled between the lumber, put some boards over myself, and sat there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then I heard, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Hurry up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Ukrainians is hollered from the tower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Hurry up, one was hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Fraction of a minute later, a number of people came, guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I could see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They couldn't see me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And couldn't-- and looked around and put more boards on top of me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They said to themselves, we have no time for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we find him later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was sitting there for hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I heard-- and later on I was told how it happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They put groups of four and six.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The men had to drop their pants so they couldn't run, just could walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it's 500 yards to the edge of the forest, which graves we dug ourselves over the months and weeks before, supposedly.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Of course, those graves were-- already had hundreds, and hundreds, and hundreds of people in over the period when the camps were created.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they put them-- they had to walk towards the edge of the grave, and then shot them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I [? bet you've ?] seen many videos, because it's basically how they do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
